Ceibo Apps Privacy Policy

Ceibo Apps respects your privacy.

Data Collection by Ceibo Apps Apps

Applications published by Ceibo Apps do not collect, store, transmit, or share personal or sensitive user data.
Ceibo Apps Privacy Policy

Ceibo Apps respects your privacy.

Data Collection by Ceibo Apps Apps

Applications published by Ceibo Apps do not collect, store, transmit, or share personal or sensitive user data.

Ceibo Apps apps:

Do not require user accounts

Do not include advertising

Do not use analytics or tracking technologies

Do not communicate with external servers operated by Ceibo Apps

All functionality operates locally on the user’s device.

If an app requests device permissions (such as camera, microphone, storage, or audio access), these permissions are used only to provide the app’s core functionality.
No data accessed through these permissions is collected, stored, or transmitted by Ceibo Apps.

Ceibo Apps does not share user data with third parties.

Google Play & Google Payments

Apps by Ceibo Apps are distributed through Google Play.

Purchases, downloads, and billing are processed by Google and are subject to Google’s privacy policies and terms. Google may independently collect and process certain information, such as:

Purchase and transaction details

Device information

Country or region

Data required for payment processing, fraud prevention, refunds, or legal compliance

Ceibo Apps does not have access to, control over, or responsibility for data collected directly by Google as part of Google Play or Google Payments services.

For more information, please review:

Google Privacy Policy

Google Play & Google Payments Privacy Notices

Changes to This Privacy Policy

If this Privacy Policy is updated, the revised version will be made available at this URL.

Contact

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact:

ceiboapps@proton.me

Last updated: 2026-01-28

